WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:00.630 --> 00:00:02.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
No! It can't be real!</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:04.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is terrible!</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:05.130 --> 00:00:06.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"At the crack of dawn,</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:06.420 --> 00:00:08.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a coup d'etat
took place in the palace.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:08.590 --> 00:00:10.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An intruder attempted
to murder the Queen</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:10.510 --> 00:00:11.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and first Princess.</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:11.890 --> 00:00:13.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Many injuries are reported."</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:14.140 --> 00:00:16.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] My mother and sister
could have died.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:16.430 --> 00:00:18.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Such violence is unacceptable!</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:18.980 --> 00:00:21.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the reality
we're living in.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:21.480 --> 00:00:23.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When the palace guards
are patrolling this far out,</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:23.900 --> 00:00:25.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you know
it isn't looking good.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:25.990 --> 00:00:28.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The whole Sovereignty
is on high alert.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:28.610 --> 00:00:30.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right now, the palace
is the last place</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:30.570 --> 00:00:31.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you want to be.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:34.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You sure you still
wanna go back there?</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:35.620 --> 00:00:37.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:38.290 --> 00:00:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should stay here until
they can capture the culprit.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:44.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's certainly an option
I'll leave on the table.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:44.710 --> 00:00:47.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I doubt
they'll be found anytime soon.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:48.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Why, because the culprit</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:48.930 --> 00:00:50.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is a member
of the royal family?</b></Default>

c0000022
00:00:51.430 --> 00:00:53.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think it could be
that Masked Lord guy?</b></Default>

c0000023
00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:55.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's hard to say, for now.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:00:56.020 --> 00:00:57.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once we're able to return
the palace,</b></Default>

c0000025
00:00:57.890 --> 00:01:00.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can use my powers
to locate the offender.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:02.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Masked Lord is aware
of my gift,</b></Default>

c0000027
00:01:02.150 --> 00:01:04.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I have a hard time
believing it's him.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:04.110 --> 00:01:05.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:05.230 --> 00:01:06.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You serious?</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:09.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your astral power
can help you locate people?</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:12.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes! Essentially,
I get to play detective.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:12.950 --> 00:01:15.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
I see. They failed the coup.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:15.370 --> 00:01:17.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you return,
you could find the culprit.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:17.450 --> 00:01:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which means the Queen</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:21.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is no longer
their primary target.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:21.210 --> 00:01:22.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'Cause if they wanna
stay hidden,</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:22.750 --> 00:01:24.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they need to take you out.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:24.380 --> 00:01:26.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm afraid your assumption
is correct.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:28.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just another reason
to stay away.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:28.550 --> 00:01:29.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For someone with a target
on their back,</b></Default>

c0000041
00:01:30.050 --> 00:01:31.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're pretty calm.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:01:31.550 --> 00:01:33.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's because
I have faith in you all.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:34.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're so close.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:01:34.970 --> 00:01:36.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you escort me
the rest of the way?</b></Default>

c0000045
00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:40.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is completely insane!</b></Default>

c0000046
00:01:40.350 --> 00:01:41.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A coup in the royal palace?</b></Default>

c0000047
00:01:41.890 --> 00:01:43.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Princess Alice?</b></Default>

c0000048
00:01:43.100 --> 00:01:44.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000049
00:01:44.190 --> 00:01:46.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The trains
are still operating, yes?</b></Default>

c0000050
00:01:46.110 --> 00:01:47.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE POLICE 203A]
Correct! We've reduced</b></Default>

c0000051
00:01:47.320 --> 00:01:48.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the number of trains,</b></Default>

c0000052
00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:50.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but the Central Province
express is still online!</b></Default>

c0000053
00:01:50.990 --> 00:01:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Thank you both.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:54.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000055
00:01:54.450 --> 00:01:55.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:01:55.910 --> 00:01:56.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Lady Alice!</b></Default>

c0000057
00:01:57.080 --> 00:01:58.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The departure time
won't change,</b></Default>

c0000058
00:01:58.620 --> 00:02:00.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if we get there early!</b></Default>

c0000059
00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:03.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You expect me
to stand around and wait?</b></Default>

c0000060
00:02:03.830 --> 00:02:06.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not what I meant,
apologies.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:02:06.590 --> 00:02:08.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
No. I'm sorry for being short.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:02:09.630 --> 00:02:11.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Am I making the right choice?</b></Default>

c0000063
00:02:11.420 --> 00:02:13.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.
You need to be with the Queen</b></Default>

c0000064
00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:15.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in this troubling time.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:02:15.300 --> 00:02:17.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I hate to say it,
they are the enemy,</b></Default>

c0000066
00:02:17.890 --> 00:02:21.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after all, but Lady Sisbell
is in good hands.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:02:21.140 --> 00:02:23.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It pains me to think
of Iska serving Sisbell</b></Default>

c0000068
00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:24.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in any capacity.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:27.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
It's fine.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:02:28.110 --> 00:02:30.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The two of us got to spend
some time together alone.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:02:31.230 --> 00:02:33.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I had a chance
to be just as close</b></Default>

c0000072
00:02:33.320 --> 00:02:34.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to him as she was!</b></Default>

c0000073
00:02:35.320 --> 00:02:36.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:02:36.450 --> 00:02:38.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Don't judge me! It's not--</b></Default>

c0000075
00:02:38.790 --> 00:02:40.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

c0000076
00:02:41.330 --> 00:02:42.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Are you all right?</b></Default>

c0000077
00:02:42.450 --> 00:02:43.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mother, hey!</b></Default>

c0000078
00:02:44.290 --> 00:02:46.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's good to hear your voice!</b></Default>

c0000079
00:02:46.670 --> 00:02:47.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They say there was a bomb</b></Default>

c0000080
00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:49.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just outside
of the throne room.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:02:49.170 --> 00:02:51.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Way too close for comfort!</b></Default>

c0000082
00:02:51.340 --> 00:02:52.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
It actually wasn't a bomb,</b></Default>

c0000083
00:02:52.590 --> 00:02:54.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but an astral art.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:02:54.220 --> 00:02:56.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We didn't find
any traces of gunpowder.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:58.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
The Sovereignty is harboring</b></Default>

c0000086
00:02:58.260 --> 00:02:59.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a ruthless traitor.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:02:59.600 --> 00:03:01.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
I'm afraid so.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:03:01.180 --> 00:03:02.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It works in our favor, though.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:03:02.730 --> 00:03:05.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bombs can be detonated
remotely from anywhere,</b></Default>

c0000090
00:03:05.140 --> 00:03:07.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but astral arts cannot.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:03:07.400 --> 00:03:10.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They have a limited range,
so the culprit is close.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:03:10.230 --> 00:03:13.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell can help us
root them out upon her return.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:03:14.070 --> 00:03:17.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When pruning a rosebush,
one is bound to bleed.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:03:17.660 --> 00:03:18.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you had any luck</b></Default>

c0000095
00:03:18.870 --> 00:03:20.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>finding your sister's
whereabouts?</b></Default>

c0000096
00:03:20.830 --> 00:03:22.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
No.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:03:22.410 --> 00:03:23.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000098
00:03:23.540 --> 00:03:25.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
You must make haste, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:03:25.210 --> 00:03:27.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please find her
and keep her safe.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:03:27.960 --> 00:03:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Of course.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:03:29.420 --> 00:03:31.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll reach out
as soon as it's possible.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:03:32.050 --> 00:03:33.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please take care.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:03:34.630 --> 00:03:35.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000104
00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:37.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so sad, Rin.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:03:37.140 --> 00:03:39.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think I've ever lied
to my mother in my life!</b></Default>

c0000106
00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:41.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, you do it all the time.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:42.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like when you want to skip out</b></Default>

c0000108
00:03:42.810 --> 00:03:43.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on your book club.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:03:43.890 --> 00:03:45.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You dramatically feign
a migraine.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:03:45.730 --> 00:03:47.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then poof,
you get to stay in bed.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:03:47.690 --> 00:03:48.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:03:48.770 --> 00:03:50.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
A slip of the tongue, My Lady.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:52.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since I have to pretend
I don't know where she is,</b></Default>

c0000114
00:03:53.190 --> 00:03:55.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need you to go out
and keep an eye on her for me.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:03:56.240 --> 00:03:57.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please stay on your toes,</b></Default>

c0000116
00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:59.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you never know
when they'll come for you.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:03:59.610 --> 00:04:01.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just be careful, okay?</b></Default>

c0000118
00:04:01.530 --> 00:04:03.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Everyone! I have great news!</b></Default>

c0000119
00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Schwartz made it all the way
to the Central Province!</b></Default>

c0000120
00:04:06.370 --> 00:04:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He should be able
to get an audience</b></Default>

c0000121
00:04:07.830 --> 00:04:09.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the Queen by tomorrow!</b></Default>

c0000122
00:04:09.130 --> 00:04:10.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With her help, we should secure</b></Default>

c0000123
00:04:10.420 --> 00:04:12.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>safe passage back
to the palace!</b></Default>

c0000124
00:04:12.540 --> 00:04:15.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's two too many
"shoulds" for my liking, dear.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:04:15.300 --> 00:04:17.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you always been
this much of a downer, Jhin?</b></Default>

c0000126
00:04:18.050 --> 00:04:19.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, all I'm trying to say is,</b></Default>

c0000127
00:04:19.800 --> 00:04:21.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don't get too excited.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:24.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You need to be thinking ahead
in case something goes wrong.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:26.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, you think
I don't know that?</b></Default>

c0000130
00:04:27.940 --> 00:04:29.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ahem.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:04:29.520 --> 00:04:30.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NENE] Would you
still like us to go out</b></Default>

c0000132
00:04:30.940 --> 00:04:32.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and patrol the perimeter?</b></Default>

c0000133
00:04:32.610 --> 00:04:34.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think patrols
will be necessary</b></Default>

c0000134
00:04:34.190 --> 00:04:36.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until Schwartz makes
contact with the Queen.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:04:36.780 --> 00:04:38.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[loud blast]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000136
00:04:38.570 --> 00:04:40.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guys?
What's happening out there?</b></Default>

c0000137
00:04:40.610 --> 00:04:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a bomb!</b></Default>

c0000138
00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:44.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Same person
who attacked the Queen?</b></Default>

c0000139
00:04:44.370 --> 00:04:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then,
we must find them, now!</b></Default>

c0000140
00:04:46.750 --> 00:04:48.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You, wanna chase them?</b></Default>

c0000141
00:04:48.290 --> 00:04:51.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. I can track them
from the safety of the hotel.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:04:56.460 --> 00:04:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Stars of fate.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:04:57.550 --> 00:05:00.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Reveal the past
I am destined to see.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:05:00.470 --> 00:05:02.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000145
00:05:05.310 --> 00:05:06.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000146
00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:07.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000147
00:05:09.390 --> 00:05:10.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gotcha.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:05:11.310 --> 00:05:12.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000149
00:05:13.060 --> 00:05:14.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all screaming]</b></Default>

c0000150
00:05:14.150 --> 00:05:15.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000151
00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:21.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell!</b></Default>

c0000152
00:05:21.950 --> 00:05:23.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You barbarian!</b></Default>

c0000153
00:05:23.570 --> 00:05:25.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All this destruction
just to find me?</b></Default>

c0000154
00:05:25.410 --> 00:05:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell! Get down!</b></Default>

c0000155
00:05:26.870 --> 00:05:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000156
00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:32.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gunshots]</b></Default>

c0000157
00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:35.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He can hit her?
From this far out?</b></Default>

c0000158
00:05:35.290 --> 00:05:38.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surrender now,
or I'll blow you away.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:05:38.260 --> 00:05:39.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's your choice.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:05:41.180 --> 00:05:43.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[evil chuckle]
Not today.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:45.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000162
00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:47.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Was that wind? No.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:05:47.850 --> 00:05:49.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's called Gravity!</b></Default>

c0000164
00:05:49.520 --> 00:05:50.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't good.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:52.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She can manipulate
the matter around--</b></Default>

c0000166
00:05:52.640 --> 00:05:53.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000167
00:05:53.850 --> 00:05:55.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000168
00:05:57.770 --> 00:05:59.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000169
00:06:03.450 --> 00:06:05.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000170
00:06:05.570 --> 00:06:06.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how?</b></Default>

c0000171
00:06:06.740 --> 00:06:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, no!
Not my neck protector!</b></Default>

c0000172
00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now what?</b></Default>

c0000173
00:06:11.210 --> 00:06:13.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Allow me to finish
what you started.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:17.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not too shabby
for a random mercenary</b></Default>

c0000175
00:06:17.300 --> 00:06:19.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she picked up off the streets.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:06:19.210 --> 00:06:20.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who could he be, Sis?</b></Default>

c0000177
00:06:20.460 --> 00:06:22.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's gotta be somebody!</b></Default>

c0000178
00:06:22.300 --> 00:06:23.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise?</b></Default>

c0000179
00:06:23.550 --> 00:06:24.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-How could you?
-[smirks]</b></Default>

c0000180
00:06:25.260 --> 00:06:27.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This will destroy the
House of Hydra's reputation!</b></Default>

c0000181
00:06:28.060 --> 00:06:29.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once everyone finds out.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:06:29.890 --> 00:06:31.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one's gonna know.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:33.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[evil chuckle]</b></Default>

c0000184
00:06:33.640 --> 00:06:34.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone...</b></Default>

c0000185
00:06:34.730 --> 00:06:36.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>stay back,
she's preparing for something.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:06:36.940 --> 00:06:38.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000187
00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:40.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[evil laugh]</b></Default>

c0000188
00:06:41.940 --> 00:06:43.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Captain Mismis.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:06:43.320 --> 00:06:45.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take Sisbell and retreat, now!</b></Default>

c0000190
00:06:45.780 --> 00:06:47.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska, no!</b></Default>

c0000191
00:06:47.200 --> 00:06:48.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing?</b></Default>

c0000192
00:06:48.370 --> 00:06:50.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE (ASTRAL)]
You never saw me at the palace!</b></Default>

c0000193
00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:51.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wouldn't have.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:52.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was only a "monster"</b></Default>

c0000195
00:06:52.500 --> 00:06:53.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who looked like this!</b></Default>

c0000196
00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:55.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Beautiful, aren't I?</b></Default>

c0000197
00:06:55.710 --> 00:06:57.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000198
00:06:58.500 --> 00:07:00.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000199
00:07:00.250 --> 00:07:03.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can do whatever I want
without being recognized now!</b></Default>

c0000200
00:07:03.590 --> 00:07:04.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000201
00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:06.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who will rally behind the Lous</b></Default>

c0000202
00:07:06.970 --> 00:07:09.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when they've yet
to defeat the Empire?</b></Default>

c0000203
00:07:09.180 --> 00:07:10.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Goodbye, House Lou!</b></Default>

c0000204
00:07:10.760 --> 00:07:13.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Sovereignty is better
off without you!</b></Default>

c0000205
00:07:14.140 --> 00:07:15.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000206
00:07:15.390 --> 00:07:16.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000207
00:07:17.100 --> 00:07:18.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can slice through my flame?</b></Default>

c0000208
00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:21.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're done here!
It's you and me.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:24.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska!</b></Default>

c0000210
00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:25.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You once told me
you were trained</b></Default>

c0000211
00:07:25.530 --> 00:07:26.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to fight mages!</b></Default>

c0000212
00:07:26.610 --> 00:07:28.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now's your chance to prove
you weren't lying!</b></Default>

c0000213
00:07:28.530 --> 00:07:29.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't lose now!</b></Default>

c0000214
00:07:29.910 --> 00:07:31.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska!</b></Default>

c0000215
00:07:31.290 --> 00:07:32.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000216
00:07:32.700 --> 00:07:36.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah...I won't lose
to an astral mage.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:07:36.870 --> 00:07:38.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But this, this is different.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:07:39.250 --> 00:07:41.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That thing isn't
your average mage.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:07:41.250 --> 00:07:42.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's a damn witch!</b></Default>

c0000220
00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:44.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000221
00:07:44.170 --> 00:07:45.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all panting]</b></Default>

c0000222
00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:48.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who was that witch?</b></Default>

c0000223
00:07:48.090 --> 00:07:50.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you two met
before tonight?</b></Default>

c0000224
00:07:50.430 --> 00:07:52.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What the hell even was she?</b></Default>

c0000225
00:07:52.350 --> 00:07:53.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
I'll tell you right now,</b></Default>

c0000226
00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:55.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this isn't what we discussed
when you hired us.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:07:56.140 --> 00:07:57.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We promised to fend
off assassins</b></Default>

c0000228
00:07:57.940 --> 00:08:00.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the Sovereignty,
not go toe-to-toe</b></Default>

c0000229
00:08:00.110 --> 00:08:01.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a flame-throwing monster.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:08:01.940 --> 00:08:03.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:08:03.690 --> 00:08:05.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise Alec Hydra
and, uh...</b></Default>

c0000232
00:08:05.780 --> 00:08:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was adopted by the House..</b></Default>

c0000233
00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:08.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By House of Hydra, and...</b></Default>

c0000234
00:08:08.740 --> 00:08:10.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[panting]
-She rounds up criminals.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:08:10.870 --> 00:08:12.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Goes on official missions
to find them all</b></Default>

c0000236
00:08:12.830 --> 00:08:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and bring them to justice.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:08:14.040 --> 00:08:15.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000238
00:08:15.410 --> 00:08:16.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But not like this.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:08:16.790 --> 00:08:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
You're telling me</b></Default>

c0000240
00:08:17.710 --> 00:08:19.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you didn't know
who she really was?</b></Default>

c0000241
00:08:19.460 --> 00:08:20.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, I didn't!</b></Default>

c0000242
00:08:20.790 --> 00:08:22.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I did, I wouldn't
have risked our lives</b></Default>

c0000243
00:08:22.460 --> 00:08:23.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>going after her!</b></Default>

c0000244
00:08:25.300 --> 00:08:26.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no more time.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:08:26.840 --> 00:08:28.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll talk about this later.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:08:28.380 --> 00:08:29.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000247
00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:31.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000248
00:08:33.760 --> 00:08:34.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, Jhin!</b></Default>

c0000249
00:08:34.850 --> 00:08:36.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think
you're doing?</b></Default>

c0000250
00:08:36.390 --> 00:08:39.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unhand me,
or I'll report you for...</b></Default>

c0000251
00:08:39.560 --> 00:08:41.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wanna do this on your own?</b></Default>

c0000252
00:08:41.190 --> 00:08:42.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000253
00:08:42.650 --> 00:08:43.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:08:44.070 --> 00:08:45.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's move out!</b></Default>

c0000255
00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:46.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000256
00:08:46.900 --> 00:08:48.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosions]</b></Default>

c0000257
00:08:48.900 --> 00:08:50.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000258
00:08:50.360 --> 00:08:52.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000259
00:08:54.830 --> 00:08:57.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000260
00:09:06.210 --> 00:09:07.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me, are you human?</b></Default>

c0000261
00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:09.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I dunno.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:09:09.090 --> 00:09:10.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you'll need
to define "human"</b></Default>

c0000263
00:09:10.880 --> 00:09:12.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for me, bodyguard!</b></Default>

c0000264
00:09:12.340 --> 00:09:13.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000265
00:09:13.930 --> 00:09:15.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000266
00:09:15.390 --> 00:09:18.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Earlier, I heard
Sis refer to you as "Iska."</b></Default>

c0000267
00:09:18.350 --> 00:09:19.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who are you, really?</b></Default>

c0000268
00:09:19.850 --> 00:09:21.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A bodyguard, remember?</b></Default>

c0000269
00:09:21.520 --> 00:09:23.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't play dumb with me.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:26.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is the Saint Disciple
of the Eleventh Seat.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:09:26.110 --> 00:09:27.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Successor of the Black Steel?</b></Default>

c0000272
00:09:27.940 --> 00:09:30.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is any of this starting
to ring a bell, Mister Nobody?</b></Default>

c0000273
00:09:31.410 --> 00:09:32.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:34.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The House of Hydra sees all.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:09:34.410 --> 00:09:36.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure, we've endured
years of misery.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:09:36.450 --> 00:09:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But now, we know
what the Empire's up to.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:09:39.410 --> 00:09:41.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You just want
to control the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:09:41.460 --> 00:09:42.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You simpleton.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:09:42.750 --> 00:09:44.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't have cast
away my humanity</b></Default>

c0000280
00:09:44.460 --> 00:09:46.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for something so trivial.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:48.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Violet Belt!</b></Default>

c0000282
00:09:49.340 --> 00:09:50.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
That all you got?</b></Default>

c0000283
00:09:50.420 --> 00:09:51.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-Don't play dumb!</b></Default>

c0000284
00:09:51.720 --> 00:09:53.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I said, "that all you got?"</b></Default>

c0000285
00:09:53.430 --> 00:09:55.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts and slices]</b></Default>

c0000286
00:09:55.850 --> 00:09:58.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You got a special weapon
there, don't ya?</b></Default>

c0000287
00:09:58.350 --> 00:10:00.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of sword cuts
through astral energy?</b></Default>

c0000288
00:10:01.640 --> 00:10:03.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hell, if I know!</b></Default>

c0000289
00:10:03.230 --> 00:10:04.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Praise of Mother Earth.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:07.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unleash your Gravity Storm!</b></Default>

c0000291
00:10:08.440 --> 00:10:09.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
What's that?</b></Default>

c0000292
00:10:10.190 --> 00:10:11.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Were they able to find Sisbell?</b></Default>

c0000293
00:10:12.070 --> 00:10:13.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She should be safe with Iska.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:10:13.860 --> 00:10:15.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin's there, too.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:10:15.110 --> 00:10:16.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WARVICK]
Lady Alice!</b></Default>

c0000296
00:10:16.330 --> 00:10:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank God you're safe!</b></Default>

c0000297
00:10:17.700 --> 00:10:19.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Kisasage! Warvick!</b></Default>

c0000298
00:10:19.700 --> 00:10:21.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You two
start evacuating the guests!</b></Default>

c0000299
00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:23.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll go find Sisbell myself!</b></Default>

c0000300
00:10:24.120 --> 00:10:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Right!
-Right!</b></Default>

c0000301
00:10:26.380 --> 00:10:27.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TRYSE]
Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:10:28.040 --> 00:10:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000303
00:10:29.840 --> 00:10:31.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have located Lady Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:34.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, the police force
was taken hostage.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:10:34.430 --> 00:10:36.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've heard that
Lady Sisbell's been hurt.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:10:38.510 --> 00:10:39.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What now?</b></Default>

c0000307
00:10:39.640 --> 00:10:42.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come with me, My Lady!
I'll take you to her!</b></Default>

c0000308
00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:46.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice?</b></Default>

c0000309
00:10:47.940 --> 00:10:50.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have something
I'd like to ask you.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:10:50.230 --> 00:10:51.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We don't have time for that!</b></Default>

c0000311
00:10:51.730 --> 00:10:54.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-She could be in danger--
-I'll be quick. Who are you?</b></Default>

c0000312
00:10:56.740 --> 00:10:58.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000313
00:11:00.950 --> 00:11:02.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE (ASTRAL)]
I've got you now.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:11:06.630 --> 00:11:07.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000315
00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:09.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000316
00:11:11.260 --> 00:11:12.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000317
00:11:13.300 --> 00:11:15.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My, you're very good!</b></Default>

c0000318
00:11:15.260 --> 00:11:17.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This should serve
as a nice little warm-up</b></Default>

c0000319
00:11:17.090 --> 00:11:19.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before I demolish
the Zoas and Lous.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:11:19.600 --> 00:11:22.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll crush you
with my special attack!</b></Default>

c0000321
00:11:22.140 --> 00:11:24.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
What is that dark sphere?</b></Default>

c0000322
00:11:24.930 --> 00:11:26.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems to be
absorbing all the light.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:11:27.520 --> 00:11:29.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whoa! A black hole?</b></Default>

c0000324
00:11:29.860 --> 00:11:31.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Correct!</b></Default>

c0000325
00:11:31.150 --> 00:11:33.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you didn't quite
answer in time.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:11:33.440 --> 00:11:34.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000327
00:11:35.030 --> 00:11:36.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Corpse Magic Bullet.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:11:37.070 --> 00:11:38.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fire!</b></Default>

c0000329
00:11:38.410 --> 00:11:39.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000330
00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:41.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] You assumed
that a princess like me</b></Default>

c0000331
00:11:41.450 --> 00:11:43.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>couldn't possibly remember
the faces</b></Default>

c0000332
00:11:43.200 --> 00:11:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of every one of her soldiers,
didn't you?</b></Default>

c0000333
00:11:45.910 --> 00:11:47.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If so, then,
you are sorely mistaken.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:49.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000335
00:11:49.540 --> 00:11:51.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know the name
and face of all who serve us.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:11:52.050 --> 00:11:54.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The House of Lou
values its people.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:11:54.090 --> 00:11:55.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000338
00:11:55.510 --> 00:11:57.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell is safe, then.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:11:57.590 --> 00:11:59.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you had her,
you wouldn't bother with me.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:12:00.010 --> 00:12:01.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000341
00:12:01.220 --> 00:12:02.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smirks]</b></Default>

c0000342
00:12:02.390 --> 00:12:03.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now move.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:12:03.680 --> 00:12:05.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A magician whose gambit
is up should know</b></Default>

c0000344
00:12:05.640 --> 00:12:07.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>better than to stick
around like this.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:12.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TRYSE] Your intelligence
is downright uncanny,</b></Default>

c0000346
00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:13.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Second Princess.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:12:14.230 --> 00:12:16.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All those brains.
And beauty, to boot.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:12:17.070 --> 00:12:18.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's kind of you.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:12:18.450 --> 00:12:21.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I am not interested
in your compliments.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:23.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you to get out
of my way.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:12:23.370 --> 00:12:25.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.
I must decline.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:12:25.540 --> 00:12:27.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
A gun? Really?</b></Default>

c0000353
00:12:27.870 --> 00:12:30.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TRYSE]
Goodbye forever, Princess.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:12:31.290 --> 00:12:33.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Is that...
-[blasts]</b></Default>

c0000355
00:12:37.340 --> 00:12:38.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000356
00:12:38.550 --> 00:12:41.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only a fool would
challenge you head-on.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:12:41.180 --> 00:12:42.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000358
00:12:45.520 --> 00:12:47.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh. I can't move!</b></Default>

c0000359
00:12:47.770 --> 00:12:49.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000360
00:12:49.100 --> 00:12:51.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] A cold-hearted
thing to do, I know.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:12:51.560 --> 00:12:52.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000362
00:12:52.810 --> 00:12:54.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TRYSE]
Aliceliese!</b></Default>

c0000363
00:12:55.110 --> 00:12:56.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000364
00:12:56.650 --> 00:12:59.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A hotel collapse
would've been disastrous.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:12:59.610 --> 00:13:01.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who knows how many casualties</b></Default>

c0000366
00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:02.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there would have been?</b></Default>

c0000367
00:13:03.330 --> 00:13:04.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TRYSE]
She stopped the explosion</b></Default>

c0000368
00:13:04.830 --> 00:13:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the very last moment?</b></Default>

c0000369
00:13:07.200 --> 00:13:09.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000370
00:13:11.210 --> 00:13:12.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000371
00:13:14.170 --> 00:13:16.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Poor thing,
I'd hate to be you.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:13:16.170 --> 00:13:18.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You didn't get crushed
and still have to fight me!</b></Default>

c0000373
00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:23.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm never going to get
crushed by an astral mage.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:13:23.640 --> 00:13:25.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll beat you no matter what!</b></Default>

c0000375
00:13:25.720 --> 00:13:28.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, you can rest easy
on that last count, at least.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:13:29.060 --> 00:13:31.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not an astral mage,
you see.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:13:31.230 --> 00:13:33.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm on a whole different
level entirely.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:13:34.360 --> 00:13:35.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000379
00:13:35.900 --> 00:13:37.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know
that's not what I meant.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:13:37.690 --> 00:13:39.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want to lose
to you at all.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:41.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I don't intend to.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:13:43.780 --> 00:13:44.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000383
00:13:45.280 --> 00:13:47.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] I understand
you're a veritable monster.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:13:48.660 --> 00:13:50.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nevertheless...</b></Default>

c0000385
00:13:50.370 --> 00:13:52.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] You may boast
about being superior</b></Default>

c0000386
00:13:52.710 --> 00:13:54.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to an astral mage.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:13:54.830 --> 00:13:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the only power
I can sense is that</b></Default>

c0000388
00:13:56.590 --> 00:13:58.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of an astral spirit.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:13:58.170 --> 00:13:59.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000390
00:13:59.380 --> 00:14:01.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew it! You see?</b></Default>

c0000391
00:14:01.510 --> 00:14:02.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't understand.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:14:04.890 --> 00:14:06.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wouldn't!</b></Default>

c0000393
00:14:06.510 --> 00:14:08.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are aware
of what the Imperial Army</b></Default>

c0000394
00:14:08.680 --> 00:14:09.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>calls me, aren't you?</b></Default>

c0000395
00:14:10.100 --> 00:14:11.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surely you have heard.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:14:11.560 --> 00:14:12.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000397
00:14:13.100 --> 00:14:15.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A normal girl calls
herself a witch.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:14:15.400 --> 00:14:17.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she means it
self-deprecatingly.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:14:17.940 --> 00:14:20.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you have no idea
what kind of person does that.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:14:20.610 --> 00:14:22.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The level of resolve
it requires.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:14:22.860 --> 00:14:24.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000402
00:14:24.620 --> 00:14:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I will not lose.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:14:26.660 --> 00:14:28.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not to someone
who has nothing more than</b></Default>

c0000404
00:14:28.330 --> 00:14:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>their physical strength!</b></Default>

c0000405
00:14:29.990 --> 00:14:31.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fire!</b></Default>

c0000406
00:14:32.120 --> 00:14:33.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000407
00:14:33.370 --> 00:14:34.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosions]</b></Default>

c0000408
00:14:40.300 --> 00:14:41.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000409
00:14:41.510 --> 00:14:43.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise!</b></Default>

c0000410
00:14:43.260 --> 00:14:44.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You little fly!</b></Default>

c0000411
00:14:46.340 --> 00:14:48.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come, astral flames!</b></Default>

c0000412
00:14:48.510 --> 00:14:50.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Release, now!</b></Default>

c0000413
00:14:50.930 --> 00:14:53.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TRYSE]
You're the Ice Calamity Witch.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:14:56.310 --> 00:14:57.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
The white sword can release</b></Default>

c0000415
00:14:57.610 --> 00:15:00.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the astral art that
the black sword slices!</b></Default>

c0000416
00:15:01.280 --> 00:15:03.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

c0000417
00:15:03.860 --> 00:15:04.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just wait.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:15:05.070 --> 00:15:08.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll see what a true
nightmare looks like.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:15:08.450 --> 00:15:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A monster far more
terrifying than me.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:15:11.160 --> 00:15:12.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Rin!</b></Default>

c0000421
00:15:12.250 --> 00:15:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shut up.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:15:13.870 --> 00:15:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
[groans]</b></Default>

c0000423
00:15:15.330 --> 00:15:16.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You let me drop!</b></Default>

c0000424
00:15:16.670 --> 00:15:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Ugh, you're alive, aren't you?</b></Default>

c0000425
00:15:18.590 --> 00:15:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, but you sound
disappointed.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:15:21.920 --> 00:15:23.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
As far as I know,</b></Default>

c0000427
00:15:23.340 --> 00:15:24.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise was a normal human</b></Default>

c0000428
00:15:24.920 --> 00:15:26.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a gravity astral spirit.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:15:28.140 --> 00:15:29.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What I don't know
is how she came to be</b></Default>

c0000430
00:15:29.970 --> 00:15:31.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that monster you just fought.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:15:31.970 --> 00:15:34.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Rin!
-Oh! Lady Alice!</b></Default>

c0000432
00:15:34.180 --> 00:15:36.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Behold, Milady,
I have successfully</b></Default>

c0000433
00:15:36.140 --> 00:15:37.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>captured the assassin!</b></Default>

c0000434
00:15:37.650 --> 00:15:39.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I did it all by myself!</b></Default>

c0000435
00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:40.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
You did not!</b></Default>

c0000436
00:15:40.820 --> 00:15:43.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?!
But what are you doing here?</b></Default>

c0000437
00:15:43.440 --> 00:15:44.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is Sisbell?</b></Default>

c0000438
00:15:44.860 --> 00:15:47.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is safe in the hands
of my team.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:15:47.200 --> 00:15:49.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Anyway, I leave her to you!
-Wait, what?</b></Default>

c0000440
00:15:49.370 --> 00:15:51.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska, don't go just yet!</b></Default>

c0000441
00:15:51.370 --> 00:15:53.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whom do you mean?</b></Default>

c0000442
00:15:53.290 --> 00:15:55.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Vichyssoise?</b></Default>

c0000443
00:15:55.410 --> 00:15:57.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is she the one behind the coup?</b></Default>

c0000444
00:15:57.330 --> 00:15:58.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000445
00:15:59.250 --> 00:16:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on, Iska.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:16:00.330 --> 00:16:02.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's one important
detail I must know.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:04.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000448
00:16:04.210 --> 00:16:06.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is she completely
in the nude?</b></Default>

c0000449
00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:07.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Sorry?
-Sorry?</b></Default>

c0000450
00:16:07.800 --> 00:16:09.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
It's just...if I, personally,</b></Default>

c0000451
00:16:09.640 --> 00:16:10.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were going to undress
in front of you,</b></Default>

c0000452
00:16:10.970 --> 00:16:12.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would make it
a much better show!</b></Default>

c0000453
00:16:12.600 --> 00:16:13.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
What are you on about?</b></Default>

c0000454
00:16:13.770 --> 00:16:15.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you even saying?</b></Default>

c0000455
00:16:15.100 --> 00:16:17.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Lady Alice,
get a hold of yourself!</b></Default>

c0000456
00:16:18.440 --> 00:16:19.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000457
00:16:19.770 --> 00:16:21.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
The Ice Calamity Witch?</b></Default>

c0000458
00:16:21.440 --> 00:16:22.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jhin, thank you.</b></Default>

c0000459
00:16:22.860 --> 00:16:24.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000460
00:16:32.160 --> 00:16:34.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right!
Be very careful, everyone!</b></Default>

c0000461
00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:35.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's really slippery!</b></Default>

c0000462
00:16:35.750 --> 00:16:37.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
I'm so sorry!</b></Default>

c0000463
00:16:37.580 --> 00:16:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER]
You little brat.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:16:38.960 --> 00:16:41.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What, are your eyes
just for show?</b></Default>

c0000465
00:16:41.080 --> 00:16:42.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, forgive me, sir!</b></Default>

c0000466
00:16:42.710 --> 00:16:44.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please accept
this coupon for some</b></Default>

c0000467
00:16:44.380 --> 00:16:45.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>excellent barbecue!</b></Default>

c0000468
00:16:46.880 --> 00:16:48.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, was this
restaurant in the Empire?</b></Default>

c0000469
00:16:49.010 --> 00:16:51.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
Boss, who are you talking to?</b></Default>

c0000470
00:16:51.680 --> 00:16:52.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS]
Um. What?</b></Default>

c0000471
00:16:54.140 --> 00:16:56.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] Just
as it happened 30 years ago.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:16:57.730 --> 00:16:58.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Millavair.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:16:58.890 --> 00:17:00.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The real monster's
coming for you.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:17:00.900 --> 00:17:03.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To sink its teeth
into your throat.</b></Default>

c0000475
00:17:03.230 --> 00:17:04.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000476
00:17:05.940 --> 00:17:08.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] Back then,
I did not even feel the cold.</b></Default>

c0000477
00:17:09.110 --> 00:17:12.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nor the sensation of fear
that grips me now.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:17:12.740 --> 00:17:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER (YOUNG)]
Milla,</b></Default>

c0000479
00:17:14.030 --> 00:17:16.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're not fit to be a Queen.</b></Default>

c0000480
00:17:16.120 --> 00:17:17.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000481
00:17:18.750 --> 00:17:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR (YOUNG)]
Really, Salinger?</b></Default>

c0000482
00:17:20.960 --> 00:17:22.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would you come
all the way here</b></Default>

c0000483
00:17:22.630 --> 00:17:25.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just to say something
horrible like that to me?</b></Default>

c0000484
00:17:25.540 --> 00:17:27.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because you're just
a little fool.</b></Default>

c0000485
00:17:27.800 --> 00:17:30.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're incapable
of ruthlessness.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:17:30.130 --> 00:17:32.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't act like a witch.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:17:32.220 --> 00:17:33.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000488
00:17:33.300 --> 00:17:34.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Let's not go there.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:17:34.850 --> 00:17:36.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was 30 years ago.</b></Default>

c0000490
00:17:36.310 --> 00:17:37.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000491
00:17:37.600 --> 00:17:39.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The reality is, I am a Queen,</b></Default>

c0000492
00:17:40.020 --> 00:17:41.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I must focus on the battle</b></Default>

c0000493
00:17:41.650 --> 00:17:42.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the Imperial Army.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:17:42.850 --> 00:17:45.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And on Alice winning
the election to secure</b></Default>

c0000495
00:17:45.270 --> 00:17:46.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the throne after me.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:17:47.860 --> 00:17:50.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am sorry, Elletear. Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:17:51.570 --> 00:17:53.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know you are both
very talented.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:17:53.620 --> 00:17:54.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000499
00:17:55.660 --> 00:17:58.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, your talents
aren't enough to rule.</b></Default>

c0000500
00:17:59.450 --> 00:18:01.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For a Queen needs
indomitable strength.</b></Default>

c0000501
00:18:02.750 --> 00:18:04.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It will be the Lous
who win this election</b></Default>

c0000502
00:18:04.580 --> 00:18:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and keep their place
on the throne.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:18:06.380 --> 00:18:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY]
On, I am shocked to say</b></Default>

c0000504
00:18:08.760 --> 00:18:10.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that for once, you have failed.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:18:10.460 --> 00:18:12.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, come now,
isn't that a bit harsh?</b></Default>

c0000506
00:18:12.760 --> 00:18:14.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My dear Lord Growley.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:18:14.470 --> 00:18:15.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000508
00:18:16.600 --> 00:18:17.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
The House of Hydra</b></Default>

c0000509
00:18:17.760 --> 00:18:19.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has shown its true colors.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:18:20.020 --> 00:18:23.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After lurking behind
the scenes for a 100 years,</b></Default>

c0000511
00:18:23.190 --> 00:18:26.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it seems they are actually
running for election.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:18:26.440 --> 00:18:29.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] You mean to tell me
they dare to challenge us?</b></Default>

c0000513
00:18:29.990 --> 00:18:31.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
Indeed.</b></Default>

c0000514
00:18:31.610 --> 00:18:34.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By framing me
as the Queen's assassin,</b></Default>

c0000515
00:18:34.660 --> 00:18:37.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they plan to eliminate us
from the race.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:18:37.620 --> 00:18:39.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They must feel confident.</b></Default>

c0000517
00:18:39.910 --> 00:18:42.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] We shall rise up
in righteous anger,</b></Default>

c0000518
00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:45.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and retaliate
with grace and poise.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:18:46.040 --> 00:18:48.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This contest will tax us all.</b></Default>

c0000520
00:18:48.170 --> 00:18:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the toughest election
in history, I've no doubt.</b></Default>

c0000521
00:18:52.090 --> 00:18:54.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Kissing.
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000522
00:18:54.430 --> 00:18:55.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Won't be long now,</b></Default>

c0000523
00:18:55.890 --> 00:18:58.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before we ask you
to shed the eye mask.</b></Default>

c0000524
00:18:58.600 --> 00:18:59.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KISSING]
Can I?</b></Default>

c0000525
00:18:59.850 --> 00:19:01.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
Oh, yes, quite soon.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:19:02.100 --> 00:19:03.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you'll use your powers</b></Default>

c0000527
00:19:03.480 --> 00:19:04.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to your heart's content.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:19:04.900 --> 00:19:06.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll cleanse planet and sun,</b></Default>

c0000529
00:19:06.860 --> 00:19:09.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before destroying the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:19:09.860 --> 00:19:12.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is time
for the moon to shine.</b></Default>

c0000531
00:19:16.110 --> 00:19:18.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's not forget
the planet and the moon.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:19:18.620 --> 00:19:19.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Knowing them as I do,</b></Default>

c0000533
00:19:19.790 --> 00:19:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've no doubt they imagine</b></Default>

c0000534
00:19:21.040 --> 00:19:22.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they will win
the coming election,</b></Default>

c0000535
00:19:22.540 --> 00:19:23.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>hands down.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:19:23.910 --> 00:19:26.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good morning to you, Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000537
00:19:26.120 --> 00:19:29.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A good morning to you,
as well, Lord Talisman.</b></Default>

c0000538
00:19:29.340 --> 00:19:31.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you so much
for having me.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:19:32.510 --> 00:19:33.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
Care for some tea?</b></Default>

c0000540
00:19:34.050 --> 00:19:36.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh no, just a little
hot water for me.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:19:36.470 --> 00:19:37.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughter]</b></Default>

c0000542
00:19:37.930 --> 00:19:40.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shall have
the finest hot water ever.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:42.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snaps finger] By the way,
your sister is faring well.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:19:42.930 --> 00:19:45.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She appears to have
a highly capable bodyguard, no?</b></Default>

c0000545
00:19:45.980 --> 00:19:47.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It never occurred to me
that Vichyssoise</b></Default>

c0000546
00:19:47.730 --> 00:19:48.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could possibly fail.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:19:48.940 --> 00:19:50.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was a small setback.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:19:50.650 --> 00:19:52.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Capable bodyguard?</b></Default>

c0000549
00:19:52.530 --> 00:19:54.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's Iska, it has to be.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:19:55.070 --> 00:19:56.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska?</b></Default>

c0000551
00:19:56.240 --> 00:19:57.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An ex-Saint Disciple.</b></Default>

c0000552
00:19:57.820 --> 00:20:00.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wouldn't it be wonderful
if he were my bodyguard?</b></Default>

c0000553
00:20:00.740 --> 00:20:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mother and Alice both
have strong astral power, see.</b></Default>

c0000554
00:20:03.830 --> 00:20:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Sisbell has adequate
astral power</b></Default>

c0000555
00:20:05.830 --> 00:20:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and now a strong bodyguard.</b></Default>

c0000556
00:20:08.580 --> 00:20:11.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And yet, look at me.
I have nothing.</b></Default>

c0000557
00:20:11.420 --> 00:20:14.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, do I sense
a little sibling rivalry?</b></Default>

c0000558
00:20:14.130 --> 00:20:15.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000559
00:20:15.420 --> 00:20:18.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all about reveling
in the spice of life for me.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:20:18.340 --> 00:20:20.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Delicacies like envy,
anger, and lust.</b></Default>

c0000561
00:20:20.640 --> 00:20:22.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I love every intense emotion,</b></Default>

c0000562
00:20:22.430 --> 00:20:24.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and savor them
like one at a feast.</b></Default>

c0000563
00:20:25.020 --> 00:20:28.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what it means.
That is, to be a witch.</b></Default>

c0000564
00:20:30.440 --> 00:20:31.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
We're leaving, Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000565
00:20:31.900 --> 00:20:33.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Time to wake up.</b></Default>

c0000566
00:20:34.150 --> 00:20:35.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:36.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was up the whole night</b></Default>

c0000568
00:20:36.490 --> 00:20:37.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while they questioned
Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000569
00:20:37.990 --> 00:20:39.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't get any sleep.</b></Default>

c0000570
00:20:39.700 --> 00:20:41.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am exhausted.</b></Default>

c0000571
00:20:42.280 --> 00:20:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, look!
It's the swordsman! See?</b></Default>

c0000572
00:20:44.540 --> 00:20:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? Wait, where?</b></Default>

c0000573
00:20:45.660 --> 00:20:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is he?
Where's Iska?</b></Default>

c0000574
00:20:48.080 --> 00:20:49.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh!
-That woke you up.</b></Default>

c0000575
00:20:49.790 --> 00:20:53.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh! Rin, I'm leaving you
in charge of Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000576
00:20:55.010 --> 00:20:57.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] I am sure Vichyssoise
is in that vehicle,</b></Default>

c0000577
00:20:57.090 --> 00:20:58.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being taken into custody.</b></Default>

c0000578
00:20:58.840 --> 00:21:00.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska.</b></Default>

c0000579
00:21:00.590 --> 00:21:03.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was Vichyssoise
a worthy opponent?</b></Default>

c0000580
00:21:03.970 --> 00:21:06.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was strong,
but something just felt weird.</b></Default>

c0000581
00:21:06.980 --> 00:21:08.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Off-putting. Eerie.</b></Default>

c0000582
00:21:09.350 --> 00:21:12.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like I couldn't get a feel
for what I was up against.</b></Default>

c0000583
00:21:12.770 --> 00:21:14.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] Are you saying
you were afraid of her?</b></Default>

c0000584
00:21:15.480 --> 00:21:17.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds kinda wimpy
for a bodyguard.</b></Default>

c0000585
00:21:18.990 --> 00:21:20.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
No.</b></Default>

c0000586
00:21:20.320 --> 00:21:21.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen a monster before.</b></Default>

c0000587
00:21:22.070 --> 00:21:25.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides Vichyssoise, I mean,
and this one was, well...</b></Default>

c0000588
00:21:25.490 --> 00:21:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's say that's how I lost
trust in the royal family.</b></Default>

c0000589
00:21:28.410 --> 00:21:29.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

c0000590
00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:32.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That thing was far
more terrifying</b></Default>

c0000591
00:21:32.710 --> 00:21:33.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000592
00:21:33.790 --> 00:21:35.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you talking about?</b></Default>

c0000593
00:21:35.590 --> 00:21:37.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] I knew as soon
as I laid eyes on it.</b></Default>

c0000594
00:21:37.710 --> 00:21:39.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That thing was pure evil.</b></Default>

c0000595
00:21:39.760 --> 00:21:42.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More twisted than
any human ever could be.</b></Default>

c0000596
00:21:43.180 --> 00:21:44.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobs]</b></Default>

c0000597
00:21:45.350 --> 00:21:47.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know
what you're feeling, Iska.</b></Default>

c0000598
00:21:47.430 --> 00:21:49.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I still tremble
just thinking about</b></Default>

c0000599
00:21:49.270 --> 00:21:51.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the night I saw that atrocity.</b></Default>

c0000600
00:21:51.850 --> 00:21:54.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's called
the Pitch-Black Monster.</b></Default>

c0000601
00:21:54.940 --> 00:21:57.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it is so foul,
one of the few creatures</b></Default>

c0000602
00:21:57.530 --> 00:21:58.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>out there that
I believe can truly</b></Default>

c0000603
00:21:59.070 --> 00:22:00.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>be called a witch.</b></Default>

c0000604
00:22:00.820 --> 00:22:03.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I simply cannot
shake off my fear of it.</b></Default>

c0000605
00:22:04.120 --> 00:22:06.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see. You've come
a long way to find me,</b></Default>

c0000606
00:22:06.780 --> 00:22:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>an Imperial soldier.</b></Default>

c0000607
00:22:08.830 --> 00:22:12.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It makes sense.
At last, I get it.</b></Default>

c0000608
00:22:13.830 --> 00:22:15.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000609
00:22:16.290 --> 00:22:20.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell, don't fret.
I'll get you home safely.</b></Default>

c0000610
00:22:23.890 --> 00:22:25.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

